		<description>A confederation of independent Foxian settlements united as a faction. They value the cooperation and protection of every member in the group above all else to strive in this harsh world. The governing body of the league is made up of a representative from each settlement and a great counselor elected by the majority of the representatives. The role of the great counselor is to tackle problems that the league is facing and propose solutions that will be voted on by the representatives. Each settlement is free to follow its own internal policies as long as it does not impinge on the values of the league. If it doesn't, the great counselor has the right to impose sanctions on the accountable settlement until they get back in line. Otherwise, the great counselor can use force to bring back order if he deems it necessary.\nThe current missions of the league are maintaining good diplomatic relations with the other non-hostile factions and using their merchants to buy advanced weaponry from their more advanced neighbors to protect its independence.</description>
